    <description>Designed by Steve Alexander and published by Millennium Games, AIR ATTACK! is a game &amp;ldquo;where you are the squadron commander of a tactical fighter squadron. Your mission - to bomb your opponent&amp;rsquo;s military targets while protecting your own. Other forces include surface-to-air missiles and an electronic warfare bomber at your disposal.&amp;rdquo; &amp;#10;This game contains rules for Basic Game and Advanced Version.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;AIR ATTACK! comes in a 8.25&amp;quot;x11.5&amp;quot;x1&amp;quot; game box with one 4-color 16&amp;quot;x21.5&amp;quot; map sheet; one counter sheet with 40 single sided die cut cardboard counters; a 16 page rulebook; and two six-sided dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game can be played by two to four players, has moderate solitaire capability, low complexity, and playing time for a game is &amp;ldquo;coffee break&amp;rdquo; short for the Basic Game, but Advanced game will run longer.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a very simple game, with fairly nice production quality. It has some chrome elements that may contribute to repeat plays. It would serve as a fairly quick and easy introduction to air wargaming for kids and adults new to wargaming.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
